cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper is about visual tracking, which is a subfield of computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also proposes a novel tracking algorithm that uses multiple features and a fusion method, which involves machine learning techniques. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely categories. The paper also involves image processing and analysis, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia) category. Finally, the paper proposes an update strategy to improve tracking performance, which involves robotics and control, and hence cs.RO (Robotics) is also a possible category.
